{"tid":1022111,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻貓到底係唔係骨折","createTime":"2019-02-14T18:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T18:34:06.000Z","uid":149563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"319308d79d591dfeffdf4e67afcca12ff4d5d055","tid":1022111,"uid":149563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T18:12:46.000Z","msg":"今日我上上下堂屋企人打電話俾我<br />\n話屋企隻貓左手好似有啲問題<br />\n我返屋企睇見佢左手唔敢用力<br />\n依家用三隻腳行<br />\n個腳型仲好似怪怪地<br />\n好似屈左落去咁<br />\n我依家好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住聽朝一夠鐘即刻打去診所book<br />\n佢平時好鍾意跳上跳落，我懷疑係佢係個籠度唔小心整親<br />\n就算佢而家屈親都仲喺度跳黎跳去<br />\n有冇ching知道佢發生咩事,到底係唔係骨折?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4748bsa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4748bsa.png&h=65a8b044&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DLD8VTR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDLD8VTR.png&h=7a7ad864&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1XCE2yS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XCE2yS.png&h=463efe1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"240a2d39a7ca8437e5b23a81c1567891821c8779","tid":1022111,"uid":27969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T18:23:10.000Z","msg":"你係咪開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5331f329ace8c5f9944c4e9ad52310557ebe88a0","tid":1022111,"uid":52511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T18:24:10.000Z","msg":"學下點對焦先"},{"pid":"ecac3afa6c6f9efeb915705c4920903e50056931","tid":1022111,"uid":172169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T18:34:06.000Z","msg":"大機會斷韌帶<br />\n快啲去診所啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}